column3: “New favorite strain, gives me that happy-go-lucky sativa feel without the heart attack like most sativa gives me. I was lucky enough to find some that also had CBD in it and it’s the only strain I’ve bought since.”
“a very nice citrus taste, light heady high. definitely recommend for anyone who has headaches or migraines.”
“OUTSTANDINGLY DELICIOUS and the high is spot on with the Leafly description.”
